snippet.title: Russian Fighter Jets Make Mock Attack on US War Ship in Black Sea

localized.description:
A Russian attack aircraft repeatedly flew near the USS Donald Cook in international waters in the Black Sea on April 12, a Pentagon spokesman said today -- Ukraine ultimatum has come and gone on Monday...
